gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 123, Raptors 103
gameRecap.excerpt: The Thunder defeated the Raptors, 123-103. Shai Gilgeous-Alexander recorded 23 points, eight assists, and seven rebounds for the Thunder, while Jalen Williams added 20 points, three rebounds, and three assists in the victory. Gradey Dick tallied 21 points and five rebounds for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Thunder win their fourth straight game and improve to 49-20, while the Raptors fall to 23-47.
